concerts here. I don't - orchestral and choral and all those and we - mother and father went to those. They always went to all those. We were always encouraged to go to everything like that, and the only real sort of entertainment you had was a sort of th
ing called Hamilton's Excursions, which was I suppose the forerunner of the pictures. And that came once a year, it was the excitement of the year and we all saved up our money to go you know at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3360220 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 Where did it come to?
