alled the Temperance Hall, it's now the Rialto. And there was still pictures you know but - remember the man with the long pointer showing then all and - it was great excite - of course it was the only thing that came you see, only - sort of entertainment
 there was, beyond the pantomime at Christmas. There'd be those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3360220 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 And you went to those?
