\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433  at the hospital sir. Not - not in my ordinary -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3360220 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 Not as a child?
