\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3360220 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 What sort of homes were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12744824 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 
Well they varied very very much. I remember one girl who was - oh she was a naughty girl, but I was very fond of her and - I went - I'd been to fetch her off Bradshawgate they used to go and parade there on a Saturday night and it wasn't very nice. An
d I'd brought her off there once or twice and she was ill and I went - do you know, they'd only two bedrooms and there were six children and I remember coming home and saying - well I judged that girl by my own standards and I - I shouldn't have done that
. I've always had a room to myself you see and - what can they have - had at that house. I think it did a lot of good. 'Cos it made you realize that people - hadn't the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15947544\charrsid7744433 amenities}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433  that you had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3360220 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 What sort of standard of living would that family have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12744824 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 Well I should think a very poor standard. Very poor. Because - as I say }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15947544\charrsid7744433 they\rquote d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433  only two rooms.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3360220 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 What sort of job would her father do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12744824 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 
He was a labourer. But - you felt you'd done - I - I met a girl - a woman rather, only a few months ago - in
 town, she came to me, she said, oh I' haven't seen you for years. And she said, you remember me being in your class at the club? So I said, yes. She said, well you know, you people that came to the club taught us that there was another way of life. And s
h
e said, you know, I - I got married and, she said, I've got both my sons through the university. And she said, I don't think I should ever have thought of it if I hadn't been taught something different you know. I don't mean that we taught them that that 
w
as it but, she said, I realised that there was - a different sort of life from what we were living. It was rather nice to feel - that. And then we taught them cookery. Then I had a dramatic class for a time. More I think to try and make them speak decent 
English and not broad {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Bolton{\*\xmlclose}. But you know the - you see they speak two languages you see. The children - the children do here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3360220 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 Now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12744824 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 
Well they always did, there's one language, one language in school and one at home. And I always remember that I 
- I - spoke to them one day and I said, now look how nicely you're speaking in this little play. Why don't you do it every day? They said, oh they'd just laugh at us at home if we did. It's rather pathetic really. 'Cos they could do it you see if they wan
ted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3360220 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9575233\charrsid7744433 Were there any clergy living around?
